# Loading libraries
```{r}
library(mdsr)
```


# Load in data
```{r}
county_results <- read.csv("countypres_2000-2016.csv")
```

# Cleaning data
Filtering for Tennessee
```{r}
county_results <- county_results %>% 
  filter(state == "Tennessee") %>% 
  select(-state_po, -office)
```
